Name: The Empanada Protocol
About the game: The Empanada Protocol is a short, but brutal presicion platformer where you play as an Empanada (A delicious piece of chilean cuisine) trying to escape the security protocol of a shady underground facility. The place is filled with traps and fun gimmicks that will test your reacction time and presicion. Do you have the will power and skill to escape? This game also includes: - Empanada de pino - Butter - Flying knives - Fun or Anger
